Symbol.Script_1D:

if gs_cont_pen=0 then gs_cont_pen=1 parameters gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen
! elevtyp: dim stElevTypes[3] stElevTypes[1] = `Сверху` stElevTypes[2] = `Сбоку` stElevTypes[3] = `Спереди`
ELEV_TOP = 1 ELEV_SIDE = 2 ELEV_FRONT = 3
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Elevation types ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
values "elevtyp" stElevTypes values "iElevTyp" 1, 2, 3
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "elevtyp" then iElevTyp = 1 if elevtyp = stElevTypes[2] then iElevTyp = 2 if elevtyp = stElevTypes[3] then iElevTyp = 3 parameters iElevTyp = iElevTyp else elevtyp = stElevTypes[1] if iElevTyp = 2 then elevtyp = stElevTypes[2] if iElevTyp = 3 then elevtyp = stElevTypes[3] parameters elevtyp = elevtyp endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Default Size ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iElevTyp" | GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "elevtyp" then if iElevTyp = ELEV_TOP then a = sizes[1][1] b = sizes[1][2] endif if iElevTyp = ELEV_SIDE then a = sizes[1][1] b = sizes[1][3] endif if iElevTyp = ELEV_FRONT then a = sizes[1][2] b = sizes[1][3] endif parameters a = a parameters b = b else if iElevTyp = ELEV_TOP then sizes[1][1] = a sizes[1][2] = b endif if iElevTyp = ELEV_SIDE then sizes[1][1] = a sizes[1][3] = b endif if iElevTyp = ELEV_FRONT then sizes[1][2] = a sizes[1][3] = b endif parameters sizes[1][1] = sizes[1][1] parameters sizes[1][2] = sizes[1][2] parameters sizes[1][3] = sizes[1][3] endif
